On Sunday the 22nd of December at 4 pm I will be taking part in a MEET AND GREET in Lebanon at @homesweethomebeirut along with @nouraridaofficial  @nathaliefanj and @mrsclueless ! The point of this gathering is to be able to gather as much help as possible to the ones in need. Everyone coming would come with something in hand such as a bag of rice, a blanket , a toy, a piece of clothing, anything small you can bring with you will make a big difference in the lives of ppl in need. 
Us girls will then be matching all the donations to double them and will be sending them out to different organisations that are helping out the poor and victims of the Lebanon crisis. 
Please be many to help as many as possible ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è
All the love 
Karen
